ğŸ› ï¸ **4. How to Build and Configure Playbooks**

Follow these steps to start creating intelligent conversational flows:

ğŸ“‹ **Step 1:** Enable Dialogflow CX and Vertex AI in Google Cloud.
ğŸ“‹ **Step 2:** Create a Conversational Agent and choose â€œBuild your own.â€
ğŸ“‹ **Step 3:** Define and configure Playbooks:

| Component        | Purpose                                            |
| ---------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
